{"tid":2220751,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"六都「被中國」 台擬退市長聯盟抗議","createTime":"2020-09-28T01:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T03:26:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4fb3590139785ef01422be26d4455982b31d68ab","tid":2220751,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T01:24:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200928/KWS5QM46YBAHLKK2RPHH45D6TI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200928%2FKWS5QM46YBAHLKK2RPHH45D6TI%2F&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=ff834745\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200928%2FKWS5QM46YBAHLKK2RPHH45D6TI%2F&h=7221f01f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200928/KWS5QM46YBAHLKK2RPHH45D6TI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n六都「被中國」 台擬退市長聯盟抗議<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/05ijuny6HAfzfVXYK5C-A-vBTGs=/2068x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/APG4PWHJFVFU5ICBVA3R7SVNQU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F05ijuny6HAfzfVXYK5C-A-vBTGs%3D%2F2068x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAPG4PWHJFVFU5ICBVA3R7SVNQU.jpg&h=924eb712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■台灣六都的國籍被歸類為「中國」，激發台灣不滿。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。，不排除退出以示抗議。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：吞特工賄款 線人無料爆  黑幫共諜案 台蘋新聞當機密<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳其邁：台非中國一部份<br />\n<br />\n「市長聯盟」是聯合國城市氣候高峯會於2014年9月所成立，由C40城市氣候變遷領導小組、地方政府永續發展理事會（ICLEI）和城市與地方政府聯盟（UCLG）等三大城市網合作組成，希望做到串聯全球城市，對抗氣候變遷。高雄市在2006年已加入ICLEI，當時不是以國籍「中國」註冊，而是以「中華台北」為名。高雄市長陳其邁稱：「台灣從來就不是中國的一部份，我們有名有姓，而且國際普遍認知、也知道高雄市是位於台灣的南部。」<br />\n<br />\n繼高雄後，台北、新北、台中、桃園及台南各市長均表明反對「被中國」，均稱市長聯盟若不改回名稱，他們考慮退出。外交部昨亦表明嚴正抗議，並已要求該組織依據台灣六都成為會員時的遞交文件名稱予以更正。台灣行政院院長蘇貞昌亦回應說：「台灣就是台灣，中國是中國，台灣不是中國的城市，如果有錯誤引用，政府都覺得非常不適當，中國希望台灣是中國的城市，這與事實不符合」。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果新聞網》"},{"pid":"97042312cb8c73586c2b502e3f79eb2360dacd49","tid":2220751,"uid":180851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T01:30:41.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"76e1f3fdbc3a7f735846b182e5ba4e19c82b11c9","tid":2220751,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T01:32:33.000Z","msg":"又係聯合国<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684045f0a845c89f55e0f5bfd83136cd99fab169","tid":2220751,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T01:36:02.000Z","msg":"企硬呀"},{"pid":"e30f8234ee9714240a1e227d68d3c2e371795c53","tid":2220751,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T02:58:44.000Z","msg":"而家用Chinese Taipei就接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e1f8cf8f5d9f5a6773432f70b7f078c7d61359","tid":2220751,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T03:26:45.000Z","msg":"吞特工賄款 線人無料爆 黑幫共諜案 台蘋新聞當機密<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}